      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk if stepping away even works anymore. it's not just the people at school, it's like... everything. i look at the future and all i see is more of this. more being judged, more being lonely, more of me just being a burden to everyone around me. it feels like there's no version of my life where it actually gets better. it just feels like a dead end.",
